+"""Rosbridge + Gazebo launcher for a single robot in selectable worlds.
 
+Supported combos:
+- robot_type:=jaka_kargo | turtlebot3
+- world_name:=no_roof_small_warehouse | small_warehouse | turtlebot3_world
+
+This launch always starts rosbridge_websocket and includes
